tokens.name: DEMX
tokens.description: The DemX is the native utility token of the DemX protocol which uses PoA consensus.  The DemX has a kind of ETF structure and backed by various precious metals which makes it easy for investors to diversify their portfolios.

tokens.name: Wrapped DEMX

tokens.name: DXAU
tokens.description: DemX Gold (DXAU) is a digital currency. Each DXAU represents one gram of physical gold. DXAU lets you spend, trade, send and earn physical gold, anywhere in the world. The circulating supply of tokens are always equalized to the stored supply in a 1:1 ratio via our smart contracts.
